flowchart LR
    A([Open Dev Mode])
    PRE{Prerequisites met?}
    FAIL[/Missing: Org plan, published library, or AI IDE/]
    B[Inspect Design]
    AUDIT[Audit component inventory]
    GAP{Any code components missing?}
    CREATE[Create missing components]
    C[[Init Code Connect]]
    GH[Connect GitHub]
    D{Select mapping method}
    NOTE_D[/UI and CLI cannot coexist on same component/]
    E((UI Mapping))
    F((CLI Mapping))
    NOTE_F[/CLI mappings are strings, not executed code/]
    SB{Storybook available?}
    SB_V[Source from story variants]
    PROPS[Validate props and variants]
    I[Map component]
    J{Preview accurate?}
    MORE{More components?}
    K[[Publish batch to MCP]]
    M[Prompt Copilot]
    N[AI scaffolds layout]
    SPEC{Scaffold matches spec?}
    NOTE_SPEC[/Treat Figma as spec, not final code generator/]
    P((Refine by section))
    QA{Passes QA?}
    PR[PR and team review]
    Q([Finalize implementation])

    A --> PRE
    PRE -->|No| FAIL
    PRE -->|Yes| B
    B --> AUDIT
    AUDIT --> GAP
    GAP -->|Yes| CREATE
    CREATE --> C
    GAP -->|No| C
    C --> GH
    GH --> D
    D -->|note| NOTE_D
    D -->|UI| E
    D -->|CLI| F
    F -->|note| NOTE_F
    F --> SB
    SB -->|Yes| SB_V
    SB_V --> PROPS
    SB -->|No| PROPS
    E --> PROPS
    PROPS --> I
    I --> J
    J -->|Adjust| I
    J -->|Accurate| MORE
    MORE -->|Yes| D
    MORE -->|No| K
    K --> M
    M --> N
    N --> SPEC
    SPEC -->|note| NOTE_SPEC
    SPEC -->|No| M
    SPEC -->|Yes| P
    P --> QA
    QA -->|No| P
    QA -->|Yes| PR
    PR --> Q
